message: /* Historical flags */ That "Xianbei flag" is certainly not real, it's just a recolor of the flag of Aichi prefecture, Japan. That Xiongnu flag is one of the flags of the "sixteen turkish empires" used in Turkey, but most of these flags are modern creations and the historical states themselves didn't use them ( see here https://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/tr_imp.html), and that Rouran flag also has no evidence, it seems to be derived from the Rouran flag used in a Europa Univeralis mod.
